sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Evaluate Page
    participant API as POST /api/v1/evaluate
    participant Eval as evaluator.py
    participant LLM as llm_evaluator.py
    participant OpenAI as GPT-5.4
    participant Store as CASES store

    UI->>API: PropertyIntake {address, city, state, zip}
    API->>Eval: evaluate_address()
    Eval->>LLM: llm_evaluate(full_address)
    alt mock_mode=false and key valid
        LLM->>OpenAI: System prompt + address
        OpenAI-->>LLM: JSON bundle
    else mock_mode or quota error
        LLM-->>LLM: _mock_evaluate(address)
    end
    LLM-->>Eval: property_facts, avm_vendors, comparables, anomalies, valuation, hypothesis
    Eval->>Eval: Wrap into domain models with provenance
    Eval->>Store: CASES[case_id] = full case
    Eval-->>API: case bundle
    API-->>UI: 200 case bundle
    UI->>UI: Display valuation range, comps, anomalies, hypothesis
